Feature: Some User Stories

Scenario: As a guest I want to display the selling list so that I can see items for sale

Scenario: As a guest I want to display details of any items so that I can see their information

Scenario: As a guest I want to sign-in with email so that I can be recognized as user

Scenario: As a user I want to have a personal area so that I can display my information

Scenario: As a user I want to be able to update my role so that I can became a seller

Scenario: As a user I want to add items to my wishlist so that I can buy its in future

Scenario: As a user I want to add items to my shopping cart so that I can buy its in future 

Scenario: As a user I want to be able to search items so that I can display specific items

Scenario: As a user I want to display meeting page of any item so that I can organize a meeting with seller of item

Scenario: As a seller I want to update my selling list so that I can add items for sale